title: The Jumble Book
creator: David Cory
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Jumble Book, by David Cory. This is a lovely collection of short stories and poems some well known others not so well known. Something to appeal to everyone. (Summary by Michele Eaton ) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
